Text: I have been divorced, and if I can help just one person avoid the trauma I have been through, it will be well worth it. I will be seeding this torrent indefinitely.
On the other hand, BitTorrent tells me that several people have downloaded this, but there's only 1 other seed out there. Come on, people! Don't hit and run!

My share ratio is 15.4, and there is only one known seed besides myself, and they're not connectable. Why is everyone so selfish? Can't you give up a few kilobytes of bandwidth to help someone's marriage?!
